name: Redux Vault
description: Redux is a system which allows users to deposit their funds into AI trading strategies. Depending on the AI trading performance, the token value can go up or down. System is accepting USDC deposits and allocates them into centralized exchanges where the money is used by the AI trading strategy. Redux token represents as share in this system, meaning, it's value will increase if the strategy is doing good, or decrease if not. Redemptions and deposits are done at an unpredicted cadence to prevent abuse.
